%p A new user has registered on the CCGD website. Here are the details:
%p
  Username: #{ @user.username }<br />
  First name: #{ @user.firstname }<br />
  Last name: #{ @user.lastname }<br />
  Email: #{ @user.email }<br />
  Phone: #{ @user.phone }<br />
  -if !@user.organization_id.nil?
    Organization: #{ @user.organization.name }<br />
  -if !@user.lab_groups.nil?
    - labgroups = @user.all_lab_groups.inject { |lgs, lg| lgs + ', ' + lg }
    Lab/group(s): #{ labgroups }<br />
